{"tid":2203780,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"JK羅琳新書被指「恐跨」 網民譏「羅琳死了」","createTime":"2020-09-15T14:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:37:05.000Z","uid":192075,"like":231,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c0f677d85c4976ea918ad2f860cdf21f374628","tid":2203780,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"創作出《Harry Potter》系列嘅JK Rowling (JK羅琳) 曾經係深受喜愛嘅作家，但近年卻因為佢不同發言之引起爭議。例如早前佢於Twitter上指，「天生有月經嘅女人先係真正嘅女人」，惹來關注跨性別族群權益人士不滿。近日佢以筆名Robert Galbraith推出《Cormoran Strike》推理小說新書，又因書中角色設定觸動網民神經，更有人於Twitter上高呼「JK Rowling死了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvbJTj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvbJTj3.jpg&h=933b8859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卻說《Cormoran Strike》系列新書《Troubled Blood》於今日 (9月15日) 發售，好快就有讀者發現書中嘅「變態連環殺人魔」，乃係一個有易服癖、鍾意作女性打扮嘅男人。雖然「變裝」同「跨性別」係兩個好唔同嘅概念，但由於「易服變態癖連環殺人犯」呢個設定本身已經<span class=\"red\">不太政治正確</span>，加上本書係由有「前科」嘅JK Rowling所作，網民就更加確信佢係「恐跨人士」，結果Twitter上出現大量「#RIPJKRowling」帖文，指JK Rowling本人雖然未死，但佢嘅事業已死。《Harry Potter》Fans更加拒絕承認該系列係由JK Rowling所寫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdE3Tkw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdE3Tkw.jpg&h=ea377b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早於2019年，JK Rowling就因為支持一名批評跨性別人士後被炒嘅女性，而被質疑「恐跨」，到今年較早時份嘅「有月經先算女人」事件，更加惹起軒然大波，結果《Harry Potter》演員如Daniel Radcliffe、Emma Watson、Rubert Grint，多個《Harry Potter》粉絲網、以及改編自《Cormoran Strike》嘅電視劇《Strike》主角之一Holliday Grainger都即刻割蓆。事後JK Rowling拎出小時候被家暴及性侵嘅事為自己解脫，又退回甘迺迪人權獎。再經過今次事件，相信佢嘅形象將會一落千丈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/153503428104387/posts/3285790354875663/?extid=N9gfTlRVtHXzbrUu&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F153503428104387%2Fposts%2F3285790354875663%2F%3Fextid%3DN9gfTlRVtHXzbrUu%26d%3Dn&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIubtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=1d662741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/153503428104387/posts/3285790354875663/?extid=N9gfTlRVtHXzbrUu&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得咁都話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲可以創作啲咩故事？<br />\n<br />\n呢單我真係覺得over咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c544ab8d89c1bf061e2e0f824a2010247e741f","tid":2203780,"uid":196924,"like":546,"dislike":1,"score":545,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就嚟俾呢啲大愛膠摧毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫返Harry Potter囉, <br />\n講Harry生完仔之後先發現自己唔適合做男人<br />\n開發新魔法進行變性<br />\n<br />\nHarry Potter and The Unwanted Penis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d33d945646adf25d5a4c1cc85bf47aa270bd09d","tid":2203780,"uid":43304,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"即刻想買本睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d821c20e9b6f9593ff8caefef83811667fe6b07a","tid":2203780,"uid":304431,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"LMSL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c582f2d2a1c278b14fe6ffb247d5395cd9a6641f","tid":2203780,"uid":61954,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"左膠=中共"},{"pid":"f91cb84d136a77040aecf750103c17f2e87ce0a6","tid":2203780,"uid":128089,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"JK羅琳本身都係左膠, 所以發生呢d事自然就唔會有正常人可憐佢。"},{"pid":"4a8962ea02662f9a83e9015e6095e08293edcea5","tid":2203780,"uid":43304,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"quote":{"pid":"f91cb84d136a77040aecf750103c17f2e87ce0a6","tid":2203780,"uid":128089,"l